OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FOne in eight pupils out of 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fschool as Covid worsens    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, About a million children in England -  
OL,6, one out of every eight pupils - were   
OL,7, off school last Thursday, as           
OL,8, Covid-related absences rose.           
OL,10,FThe official figures also show staffing
OL,11,Fproblems worsening, with a quarter of  
OL,12,Fschools seeing teachers and leaders'   
OL,13,Fabsence rates above 15%.               
OL,15,FAcross England as a whole, about 9% of 
OL,16,Fteachers were absent.                  
OL,18,FEducation Secretary Nadhim Zahawi says 
OL,19,Fhe is giving schools what they need to 
OL,20,Fkeep pupils in class.                  
